00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:56.620
And that's the non-conservative
force that does the work.

00:03:56.620 --> 00:03:59.460
So the main point was,
electrostatics is conservative,

00:03:59.460 --> 00:04:03.538
and yet when a charge goes
around and around the loop,

00:04:03.538 --> 00:04:07.030
the line integral of the total
force is not 0,

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:09.508
so it's not entirely driven by
electrostatics,

00:04:09.508 --> 00:04:11.500
but electrostatic forces are
important.

00:04:11.500 --> 00:04:15.293
Just like gravity's important
here, because gravity's what

00:04:15.293 --> 00:04:17.089
helps you come down here.
 

00:04:17.089 --> 00:04:22.005
The ski lift is all hidden
inside, and then it takes you

00:04:22.005 --> 00:04:22.899
back up.
 

00:04:22.899 --> 00:04:25.286
So I'm going to draw the
circuit in a way that really

00:04:25.286 --> 00:04:27.028
