this,

00:06:23.028 --> 00:06:26.545
and maybe there's a switch
here, you can be assured that

00:06:26.545 --> 00:06:28.910
between this point and this
point,

00:06:28.910 --> 00:06:30.910
if you go around and measure
the voltage difference,

00:06:30.910 --> 00:06:33.579
that will be the emf of the
battery.

00:06:33.579 --> 00:06:35.920
That's all you really need to
know.

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:39.052
The way it comes out is that
this battery is like a pump that

00:06:39.052 --> 00:06:42.079
